WEBVTT

00:01:55.459 --> 00:01:57.159
Big stars really are different.

00:01:57.379 --> 00:01:59.519
Don't just look at how unrealistically handsome he is on TV.

00:01:59.859 --> 00:02:01.219
But looking closely like this...

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:03.659
He looks even less real than on TV.

00:02:03.819 --> 00:02:04.959
Nothing to be surprised about.

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.500
Stars are people too.

00:02:07.319 --> 00:02:08.539
Oh my god.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.719
So handsome.

00:02:11.740 --> 00:02:12.580
These kids...

00:02:12.659 --> 00:02:14.199
since when did they learn to climb windows?

00:02:14.460 --> 00:02:15.379
Auntie Cai.

00:02:15.439 --> 00:02:16.860
One of Ms. Liu's students is here.

00:02:16.939 --> 00:02:17.659
Guess who it is.

00:02:17.819 --> 00:02:18.360
Who?

00:02:18.699 --> 00:02:20.000
Zhang Tianyu.

00:02:21.060 --> 00:02:22.280
Zhang Tianyu?

00:02:22.819 --> 00:02:23.719
Don't know him.

00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:24.719
Zhang Tian...

00:02:25.659 --> 00:02:27.860
How could you not know Zhang Tianyu?

00:02:27.860 --> 00:02:29.060
He's a big star!

00:02:29.199 --> 00:02:30.620
How old is he? Does he have a partner?

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:31.979
Auntie Cai,

00:02:32.199 --> 00:02:34.139
stars don't need you to set them up.

00:02:34.219 --> 00:02:35.099
Right.

00:02:35.180 --> 00:02:36.560
Stars have to stay single.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.360
Make room, let me see.

00:02:38.479 --> 00:02:39.219
Move over.

00:02:39.219 --> 00:02:39.780
Let me have a look.

00:02:44.639 --> 00:02:45.759
Tianyu.

00:02:49.180 --> 00:02:49.979
Back then,

00:02:50.219 --> 00:02:52.120
in your class of students,

00:02:52.580 --> 00:02:53.520
the one I had the least...

00:02:54.060 --> 00:02:55.379
hope for was you.

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:58.580
I mean, aside from having a good image,

00:02:58.939 --> 00:03:01.699
your lines, movement, voice...

00:03:01.780 --> 00:03:02.099
right?

00:03:02.099 --> 00:03:03.120
Especially that head of yours,

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:05.580
you were completely dense.

00:03:06.039 --> 00:03:07.639
Who would have thought?

00:03:07.759 --> 00:03:08.840
Look at you now.

00:03:09.139 --> 00:03:10.439
The most successful one...

00:03:10.500 --> 00:03:12.280
is actually you.

00:03:12.680 --> 00:03:14.520
It must be talent plus hard work.

00:03:17.199 --> 00:03:18.099
Our Tianyu...

00:03:18.159 --> 00:03:20.419
is really super hardworking.

00:03:20.759 --> 00:03:22.240
Just to maintain this figure,

00:03:23.060 --> 00:03:24.819
gym, running, dieting, inducing vomiting...

00:03:24.919 --> 00:03:25.699
Ev...

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:28.199
That last one isn't true!

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:29.039
Good that it's not.

00:03:30.060 --> 00:03:31.060
In short,

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:31.860
Tianyu

00:03:31.900 --> 00:03:34.099
is really tough on himself.

00:03:34.580 --> 00:03:35.620
Otherwise, that recent...

00:03:35.620 --> 00:03:36.860
latest season of Running Man...

00:03:36.900 --> 00:03:38.520
how would they have picked our Tianyu?

00:03:39.139 --> 00:03:39.879
Is that so?

00:03:40.479 --> 00:03:41.159
That's great.

00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:42.439
That is really great.

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.039
There is one thing,

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:47.680
your teacher has to remind you of.

00:03:48.599 --> 00:03:49.439
Young people...

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.159
when it comes to relationships between men and women,

00:03:53.479 --> 00:03:54.939
you must control yourself.

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:56.500
Don't be too casual.

00:03:56.900 --> 00:03:58.199
You mustn't mess around.

00:03:58.259 --> 00:03:59.800
With social media these days,

00:03:59.860 --> 00:04:00.780
the slightest thing...

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:01.919
gets you exposed.

00:04:01.919 --> 00:04:02.819
You know, how...

00:04:02.819 --> 00:04:03.800
Ms. Liu,

00:04:04.099 --> 00:04:05.400
is it that these past two days...

00:04:05.479 --> 00:04:06.680
you heard some...

00:04:06.759 --> 00:04:07.800
rumors or something?

00:04:07.800 --> 00:04:08.419
Is that it?

00:04:10.020 --> 00:04:13.080
You absolutely must not believe the nonsense on social media.

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:14.360
Saying our Tianyu is...

00:04:14.639 --> 00:04:15.680
with so-and-so...

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:16.560
doing this and that.

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:17.300
Let me tell you,

00:04:17.939 --> 00:04:19.639
it's all completely fabricated.

00:04:20.540 --> 00:04:21.319
Just chasing clout.

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:23.180
I get it.

00:04:24.279 --> 00:04:25.399
Just ordinary audiences,

00:04:26.420 --> 00:04:27.519
following shows and stars,

00:04:28.540 --> 00:04:29.579
enjoying the gossip and scoops.

00:04:31.220 --> 00:04:32.959
A bit like our Little Cai here.

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:34.860
Who is Little Cai?

00:04:35.100 --> 00:04:36.399
Here I am!

00:04:36.399 --> 00:04:37.639
See? As soon as I mention Little Cai,

00:04:37.639 --> 00:04:38.660
Little Cai arrives.

00:04:40.079 --> 00:04:41.879
This must be that famous heartthrob, right?

00:04:41.879 --> 00:04:42.360
Yes.

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:44.060
He's really good-looking.

00:04:44.060 --> 00:04:45.120
Just like a young girl.

00:04:46.220 --> 00:04:46.860
Tianyu.

00:04:47.040 --> 00:04:48.100
It's about time.

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:48.779
Right.

00:04:48.779 --> 00:04:49.319
Ms. Liu.

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:50.579
We came here today

00:04:50.579 --> 00:04:51.660
mainly to thank you

00:04:51.660 --> 00:04:53.639
for educating and nurturing me.

00:04:53.860 --> 00:04:55.779
And also to wish you a Happy Teachers' Day.

00:04:56.220 --> 00:04:57.180
Thank you.

00:04:57.180 --> 00:04:57.879
The gift.

00:04:57.920 --> 00:04:58.759
Here.

00:04:58.759 --> 00:05:00.079
Look at that, so thoughtful.

00:05:00.100 --> 00:05:01.339
You shouldn't have, really.

00:05:01.339 --> 00:05:02.399
What a good kid.

00:05:02.620 --> 00:05:03.899
Well, we've disturbed you for so long,

00:05:03.899 --> 00:05:04.720
we should head back now.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:05.240
We're taking off.

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:05.639
Okay.

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:06.699
Happy holiday.

00:05:06.699 --> 00:05:07.259
Let's go.

00:05:07.540 --> 00:05:08.060
Don't go just yet.

00:05:08.379 --> 00:05:09.860
The business between you two,

00:05:09.939 --> 00:05:10.879
surely you're done talking, right?

00:05:10.959 --> 00:05:11.259
Yes.

00:05:11.259 --> 00:05:11.699
We...

00:05:11.939 --> 00:05:12.839
are done talking.

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:14.899
Children,

00:05:15.019 --> 00:05:15.779
come on in.

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:17.660
Zhang Tianyu!

00:05:17.660 --> 00:05:19.720
My idol, Zhang Tianyu!

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.579
I like you so much!

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:23.220
So handsome!

00:05:23.519 --> 00:05:24.160
Come on,

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:24.740
one by one.

00:05:24.740 --> 00:05:25.699
I'll take photos for you.

00:05:25.899 --> 00:05:26.699
Take photos.

00:05:31.379 --> 00:05:32.420
Teacher's Day is here

00:05:32.459 --> 00:05:34.079
Students are coming to visit Ms. Liu

00:05:34.379 --> 00:05:35.420
It's only natural

00:05:36.360 --> 00:05:37.160
Grandpa Li

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:38.620
You don't understand

00:05:39.319 --> 00:05:40.379
This Zhang Tianyu

00:05:40.439 --> 00:05:41.899
he is a top celebrity now

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:42.560
He came

00:05:42.779 --> 00:05:44.680
chatted with Grandma Liu for half an hour

00:05:44.759 --> 00:05:46.079
and when leaving our retirement community

00:05:46.180 --> 00:05:47.399
he was stuck for two hours

00:05:47.500 --> 00:05:49.079
Traffic was completely paralyzed

00:05:49.220 --> 00:05:50.899
Ms. Liu has worked hard all her life

00:05:51.079 --> 00:05:52.779
Having such an outstanding student

00:05:53.079 --> 00:05:54.180
is quite normal

00:05:54.959 --> 00:05:55.879
Grandpa Li, look

00:05:56.060 --> 00:05:57.680
I even got an autograph

00:05:58.500 --> 00:05:59.779
What is written here?

00:06:00.220 --> 00:06:00.879
Zhang what?

00:06:00.920 --> 00:06:02.000
Zhang Tianyu

00:06:02.100 --> 00:06:03.360
He wrote in English

00:06:04.220 --> 00:06:05.139
A Chinese person

00:06:05.420 --> 00:06:06.579
why sign an English name?

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:08.019
Grandpa Li

00:06:08.079 --> 00:06:09.319
you don't understand

00:06:10.079 --> 00:06:11.120
This is something he

00:06:11.300 --> 00:06:12.379
paid someone

00:06:12.459 --> 00:06:13.720
to design specially

00:06:14.259 --> 00:06:15.720
Just these ghostly scribbles?

00:06:16.199 --> 00:06:17.560
I can draw three in a moment

00:06:18.180 --> 00:06:19.120
Wouldn't I become a ghost?

00:06:19.980 --> 00:06:20.980
Grandpa Li

00:06:21.060 --> 00:06:22.120
you don't understand

00:06:22.860 --> 00:06:24.379
You keep saying "I don't understand"

00:06:24.459 --> 00:06:25.379
What does that mean?

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:28.199
Just like those students of mine back then

00:06:28.620 --> 00:06:30.180
idling about all day long

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:32.879
chasing those Hong Kong and Taiwan stars

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:34.220
You aren't a teacher

00:06:34.220 --> 00:06:35.600
where would you get students?

00:06:35.699 --> 00:06:36.839
I'm not a teacher

00:06:37.319 --> 00:06:39.079
but that didn't stop my subordinates

00:06:39.199 --> 00:06:41.120
from respecting me like a teacher

00:06:41.759 --> 00:06:43.120
During festivals

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:45.579
they would bring tea and fruits

00:06:45.579 --> 00:06:47.060
and boxes of pastries to see me

00:06:47.379 --> 00:06:48.019
So annoying

00:06:51.540 --> 00:06:53.360
Unlike certain people

00:06:54.339 --> 00:06:56.139
who were teachers all their lives

00:06:57.199 --> 00:06:58.220
Teacher's Day is here

00:06:59.180 --> 00:07:00.759
and not a single visitor

00:07:04.740 --> 00:07:06.139
Unlike certain people

00:07:06.620 --> 00:07:08.220
who were teachers all their lives

00:07:08.779 --> 00:07:10.139
Teacher's Day is almost here

00:07:10.759 --> 00:07:12.660
and not a single person comes to visit

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:17.699
Why don't you refute me?

00:07:19.100 --> 00:07:20.259
You just don't understand

00:07:21.259 --> 00:07:22.600
Why do you all say that?

00:07:23.459 --> 00:07:25.259
It would be better if no one came

00:07:25.339 --> 00:07:26.060
Look

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:26.740
The visit

00:07:26.740 --> 00:07:27.519
isn't it here?

00:07:28.399 --> 00:07:29.639
Someone really came to see you?

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:31.079
Let me see

00:07:31.579 --> 00:07:32.079
Don't

00:07:32.220 --> 00:07:33.319
You really aren't polite, are you?

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:34.680
Didn't you tell me to look?

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:37.480
What is written here?

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:38.459
It's all messy

00:07:43.639 --> 00:07:44.980
Which country is your student from?

00:07:45.519 --> 00:07:46.360
Why didn't he write Chinese characters?

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:47.379
He went straight for Pinyin?

00:07:47.379 --> 00:07:48.199
He's Chinese

00:07:48.879 --> 00:07:50.459
He wrote in Cantonese

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.480
Grandpa Fan

00:07:57.660 --> 00:07:58.779
What does this mean?

00:07:58.839 --> 00:08:00.120
Translate it for us.

00:08:00.860 --> 00:08:02.139
His student says...

00:08:02.639 --> 00:08:04.079
He's coming to visit him.

00:08:04.579 --> 00:08:05.920
But not to pay his respects.

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:08.040
Don't expect a box of pastries or anything.

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:10.279
He's coming to settle a score.

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:12.660
Because back then...

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:14.160
When he was in school...

00:08:14.220 --> 00:08:16.100
Professor Fan bullied him.

00:08:16.100 --> 00:08:16.600
Bul...

00:08:17.459 --> 00:08:18.060
Wait, no.

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:20.199
That little bit translated into all that?

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:23.000
Cantonese is amazing.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:23.819
Isn't it just?

00:08:23.860 --> 00:08:24.500
Old Li.

00:08:24.839 --> 00:08:26.240
Do you really know Cantonese?

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:27.220
I do.

00:08:28.339 --> 00:08:29.779
Like hell I do.

00:08:31.339 --> 00:08:32.759
Then how did you know just now...

00:08:32.759 --> 00:08:34.519
about him coming to settle a score?

00:08:34.940 --> 00:08:35.820
I guessed it.

00:08:37.500 --> 00:08:38.340
Did you really...

00:08:38.720 --> 00:08:39.820
bully him back then?

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:41.159
Who?

00:08:41.480 --> 00:08:42.500
Back then, I was...

00:08:44.059 --> 00:08:44.840
You wouldn't understand.

00:08:46.159 --> 00:08:47.620
Again with the "I wouldn't understand"?

00:08:48.019 --> 00:08:48.899
I don't understand.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.519
Fine, I don't understand.

00:08:51.899 --> 00:08:52.879
What don't I understand?

00:08:52.879 --> 00:08:53.700
You understand.

00:08:54.539 --> 00:08:55.620
I don't understand.

00:09:01.639 --> 00:09:02.639
See for yourself.

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:04.840
Which one is your...

00:09:04.919 --> 00:09:05.960
Teacher?

00:09:06.120 --> 00:09:06.759
Okay.

00:09:08.419 --> 00:09:09.460
Excuse me, who are you looking for?

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:11.120
Teacher.

00:09:11.720 --> 00:09:12.340
My surname is Li.

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:13.019
Not Xi.

00:09:13.080 --> 00:09:13.940
We don't have anyone named Xi here.

00:09:13.980 --> 00:09:14.860
You've got the wrong person.

00:09:15.639 --> 00:09:17.440
You are my teacher.

00:09:17.519 --> 00:09:19.320
I am your student.

00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:21.399
I am He Ziqiang.

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:22.200
He Jiqiang?

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:25.179
I've mentored many juniors...

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:27.259
but never a He Jiqiang.

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:29.519
Not He Jiqiang.

00:09:29.639 --> 00:09:31.399
It's He Ziqiang.

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:33.580
"Zi" as in "oneself".

00:09:34.820 --> 00:09:36.620
He Ziqiang.

00:09:36.620 --> 00:09:37.960
Remember now?

00:09:38.059 --> 00:09:38.740
Still no.

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:42.480
I'm the one you hated the most!

00:09:43.340 --> 00:09:44.659
The one you hated the most?

00:09:44.980 --> 00:09:46.200
Then it might be him.

00:09:46.980 --> 00:09:47.940
He's quite hateable.

00:09:48.379 --> 00:09:49.539
Teacher.

00:09:49.740 --> 00:09:52.059
Thank you for taking care of me all those years.

00:09:52.059 --> 00:09:52.860
No, wait a minute.

00:09:52.860 --> 00:09:54.059
Who are you?

00:09:54.879 --> 00:09:55.799
Teacher.

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:58.059
How can you not remember me?

00:09:58.139 --> 00:09:59.940
I don't know you at all.

00:10:00.019 --> 00:10:01.899
Besides, I've never been a teacher.

00:10:02.980 --> 00:10:04.279
Is he looking for Ms. Liu?

00:10:04.279 --> 00:10:06.179
She has students all over the world.

00:10:06.179 --> 00:10:07.200
Teacher.

00:10:07.940 --> 00:10:08.379
You...

00:10:08.639 --> 00:10:09.580
Wait, that's not right.

00:10:09.820 --> 00:10:11.379
The gender is wrong.

00:10:11.559 --> 00:10:14.220
My teacher is a man.

00:10:14.419 --> 00:10:16.100
And his surname isn't Liu.

00:10:16.159 --> 00:10:17.460
His surname is Fan.

00:10:17.559 --> 00:10:18.659
Surname Huan? Huan?

00:10:18.740 --> 00:10:19.399
Yes.

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:21.179
There's no surname Huan in the Book of Surnames.

00:10:21.179 --> 00:10:21.620
That's right.

00:10:21.679 --> 00:10:22.480
It's the one...

00:10:22.559 --> 00:10:24.220
The Fan as in "meal".

00:10:24.639 --> 00:10:25.620
Fan!

00:10:26.259 --> 00:10:27.399
It's Professor Fan.

00:10:27.419 --> 00:10:28.220
Old Fan.

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:29.120
Old Fan is...

00:10:29.779 --> 00:10:30.139
Old...

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:31.419
Where's Old Fan?

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:47.059
What is this?

00:10:47.480 --> 00:10:48.580
I'm not dead yet.

00:10:49.559 --> 00:10:50.279
Teacher.

00:10:50.899 --> 00:10:51.600
It seems

00:10:51.779 --> 00:10:54.200
you still can't let go of the past with me.

00:10:55.519 --> 00:10:56.100
Say it.

00:10:57.580 --> 00:10:59.019
What do I have to do

00:10:59.100 --> 00:11:00.919
for you to forgive yourself?

00:11:01.080 --> 00:11:02.240
You should just...

00:11:03.679 --> 00:11:05.480
Why should I forgive myself?

00:11:06.179 --> 00:11:06.940
What a joke.

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:08.220
Back then,

00:11:08.679 --> 00:11:10.379
did I do anything to wrong you?

00:11:10.879 --> 00:11:11.960
No.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:14.519
It's precisely because

00:11:14.779 --> 00:11:16.539
of your strict teachings, Teacher,

00:11:16.659 --> 00:11:18.419
that I am where I am today.

00:11:18.840 --> 00:11:19.980
Where you are today?

00:11:20.980 --> 00:11:22.100
I forgot to ask.

00:11:22.899 --> 00:11:24.159
Where are you currently

00:11:25.039 --> 00:11:26.299
holding a high position?

00:11:26.379 --> 00:11:27.259
Teacher,

00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:30.000
you've finally asked that question.

00:11:32.519 --> 00:11:33.679
To be honest, Teacher,

00:11:34.340 --> 00:11:35.580
I am the owner of five

00:11:35.639 --> 00:11:39.320
listed companies worth over a hundred million.

00:11:40.080 --> 00:11:41.879
Just the employees under me

00:11:42.080 --> 00:11:43.700
number over twenty thousand.

00:11:44.659 --> 00:11:45.440
Professor Fan,

00:11:46.700 --> 00:11:47.980
your prophecy

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:50.179
didn't come true.

00:11:51.559 --> 00:11:52.159
I...

00:11:52.159 --> 00:11:52.759
I understand.

00:11:52.759 --> 00:11:53.659
I get it now.

00:11:54.279 --> 00:11:55.419
You coming here today

00:11:55.419 --> 00:11:56.320
isn't to visit me.

00:11:56.500 --> 00:11:58.019
It's specifically to show off to me.

00:11:58.100 --> 00:11:58.960
You're here to demonstrate your power.

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:00.220
Teacher,

00:12:01.399 --> 00:12:02.620
I'm just here to

00:12:02.700 --> 00:12:03.919
report to you

00:12:04.519 --> 00:12:05.460
on these years,

00:12:05.480 --> 00:12:08.700
and the tiny little achievements I've made.

00:12:09.019 --> 00:12:10.700
I don't accept your provocation.

00:12:11.500 --> 00:12:12.059
Go.

00:12:12.139 --> 00:12:13.259
Please leave here.

00:12:13.259 --> 00:12:13.940
No, Teacher...

00:12:13.940 --> 00:12:14.919
And these gifts...

00:12:14.919 --> 00:12:15.539
No.

00:12:15.799 --> 00:12:16.720
Take them all away.

00:12:16.879 --> 00:12:17.360
Go.

00:12:17.500 --> 00:12:18.059
Teacher...

00:12:18.740 --> 00:12:19.440
And this too.

00:12:20.820 --> 00:12:21.419
Go!

00:12:22.139 --> 00:12:23.120
I don't mean to criticize you,

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:25.659
but you've always been like this.

00:12:25.659 --> 00:12:27.200
Pig-headed and unreasonable.

00:12:27.519 --> 00:12:28.720
A student finally comes to visit,

00:12:28.919 --> 00:12:30.059
and you chased him away.

00:12:30.159 --> 00:12:30.820
Alright.

00:12:30.820 --> 00:12:32.120
You don't understand anything.

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:33.419
This student...

00:12:36.259 --> 00:12:37.179
Here we go again.

00:12:37.879 --> 00:12:39.159
So say it.

00:12:39.500 --> 00:12:40.519
Do I have to chase you for answers?

00:12:40.759 --> 00:12:41.659
Yeah, what actually happened?

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:42.899
Right.

00:12:42.980 --> 00:12:45.019
Back then, the kid was just a kid.

00:12:45.019 --> 00:12:46.419
How big of a sin could he have committed?

00:12:46.620 --> 00:12:47.720
This kid...

00:12:49.059 --> 00:12:50.240
cheated on an exam back then.

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:52.059
I caught him in the act and he was expelled.

00:12:52.620 --> 00:12:54.159
That is a question of character.

00:12:54.519 --> 00:12:56.519
That has to be dealt with strictly anywhere.

00:12:57.419 --> 00:12:59.840
Couldn't you have been more tactical back then?

00:13:00.059 --> 00:13:01.379
This kid definitely holds a grudge.

00:13:02.019 --> 00:13:03.860
He's pinned this whole debt on you.

00:13:04.379 --> 00:13:05.200
He just said

00:13:05.840 --> 00:13:06.919
he's coming back tomorrow.

00:13:08.019 --> 00:13:09.299
Tomorrow...

00:13:10.399 --> 00:13:12.700
His expulsion was the college's decision.

00:13:12.799 --> 00:13:14.559
I even kept suggesting

00:13:14.659 --> 00:13:16.299
to change it to a demerit.

00:13:16.759 --> 00:13:18.200
He's coming back tomorrow.

00:13:18.220 --> 00:13:19.659
Will he take revenge on me?

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:21.159
You guys help me think of a way.

00:13:21.159 --> 00:13:22.059
Don't worry.

00:13:22.600 --> 00:13:24.000
Leave this to me.

00:13:24.519 --> 00:13:26.419
Tomorrow, listen to me for everything.

00:13:26.639 --> 00:13:27.200
Meeting adjourned.

00:13:29.620 --> 00:13:30.360
Meeting adjourned.

00:13:31.299 --> 00:13:32.620
Shouldn't I be the one announcing that?

00:13:37.179 --> 00:13:37.940
It's broad daylight

00:13:38.179 --> 00:13:39.220
why are you wearing sunglasses?

00:13:39.299 --> 00:13:40.159
Auntie Cai said

00:13:40.259 --> 00:13:41.360
it looks stylish

00:13:44.259 --> 00:13:45.019
It's scorching hot

00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:46.320
why are you wearing a scarf?

00:13:46.440 --> 00:13:47.360
Auntie Cai said

00:13:47.419 --> 00:13:48.480
it has an aura

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:49.379
Come on

00:13:52.399 --> 00:13:53.460
I'm not crippled or paralyzed

00:13:53.460 --> 00:13:54.419
why sit in a wheelchair?

00:13:54.460 --> 00:13:55.340
Auntie Cai said

00:13:55.399 --> 00:13:56.299
it looks imposing

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:56.779
Come on

00:13:56.779 --> 00:13:57.679
Come, let's go

00:13:57.759 --> 00:13:59.059
Little Cai is acting so mysterious

00:13:59.059 --> 00:14:00.419
what exactly is the plan?

00:14:00.460 --> 00:14:01.320
Auntie Cai said

00:14:01.379 --> 00:14:02.600
first, Grandpa Li,

00:14:02.600 --> 00:14:04.080
Uncle Liang, and herself

00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:05.539
will block the courtyard gate

00:14:05.559 --> 00:14:06.820
to keep He Jiqiang...

00:14:06.820 --> 00:14:10.259
that He Ziqiang out of our territory

00:14:10.299 --> 00:14:11.559
reason with him

00:14:11.639 --> 00:14:12.799
and move him with emotion

00:14:13.000 --> 00:14:15.039
Then, when they're just about done

00:14:15.120 --> 00:14:16.960
I'll push you out like this

00:14:17.019 --> 00:14:19.080
the enemy will surely retreat

00:14:19.139 --> 00:14:20.159
without a fight

00:14:21.759 --> 00:14:22.360
Okay

00:14:25.679 --> 00:14:26.620
Excuse me, where are you going?

00:14:28.059 --> 00:14:29.399
Sir

00:14:29.559 --> 00:14:31.120
we've met before

00:14:31.539 --> 00:14:33.299
I'm here to find my teacher

00:14:33.480 --> 00:14:34.840
Mr. Fan

00:14:36.200 --> 00:14:37.480
Halt

00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:40.100
You want to see Mr. Fan

00:14:40.960 --> 00:14:42.299
but Mr. Fan doesn't want to see you

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:44.759
Mr. Fan told me to tell you...

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:47.100
About face

00:14:48.620 --> 00:14:50.120
If you don't obey orders, I'll call security

00:14:51.700 --> 00:14:52.879
Sir

00:14:53.120 --> 00:14:53.440
you...

00:14:53.799 --> 00:14:56.379
you have to hear me out

00:14:56.700 --> 00:14:58.259
After I've explained

00:14:58.340 --> 00:14:59.159
I promise...

00:14:59.220 --> 00:15:01.480
About face, quick march

00:15:02.019 --> 00:15:02.720
Fine

00:15:03.759 --> 00:15:05.220
I need to know the ins and outs

00:15:05.720 --> 00:15:07.419
I can't just listen to Old Fan's side of the story

00:15:07.919 --> 00:15:08.399
right?

00:15:08.460 --> 00:15:08.840
Come

00:15:08.899 --> 00:15:09.340
sit down

00:15:09.700 --> 00:15:10.480
let's have a chat, man to man

00:15:11.159 --> 00:15:12.059
Okay

00:15:13.360 --> 00:15:13.840
Zhu Zhu

00:15:15.159 --> 00:15:16.139
push me out

00:15:16.740 --> 00:15:18.720
Let's see how Mr. Li's psychological warfare

00:15:18.720 --> 00:15:19.759
is coming along

00:15:25.559 --> 00:15:26.940
That's really Old Fan's fault

00:15:27.659 --> 00:15:28.879
how could he say such a thing?

00:15:29.399 --> 00:15:31.519
But he is my teacher after all

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:33.500
If between the two of us

00:15:33.500 --> 00:15:35.559
one must bow their head and apologize

00:15:35.919 --> 00:15:38.200
then I can only sacrifice myself

00:15:40.919 --> 00:15:42.559
What a good student

00:15:43.340 --> 00:15:44.600
hard to find these days

00:15:45.299 --> 00:15:45.720
Let's go

00:15:46.679 --> 00:15:47.360
follow me into the yard

00:15:49.559 --> 00:15:51.139
Is this appropriate?

00:15:51.620 --> 00:15:54.019
Didn't my teacher send you to stop me?

00:15:54.759 --> 00:15:56.159
He send me?

00:15:56.700 --> 00:15:57.700
What a joke

00:15:57.919 --> 00:15:59.000
I outrank him

00:15:59.059 --> 00:16:00.139
Let's go, follow me in

00:16:06.860 --> 00:16:07.600
Come, Little He.

00:16:08.059 --> 00:16:08.759
Sit here.

00:16:09.379 --> 00:16:10.259
Wait a minute.

00:16:12.500 --> 00:16:13.480
I told you to stop him.

00:16:13.480 --> 00:16:14.700
Why did you invite him in?

00:16:15.120 --> 00:16:16.700
What's wrong with having a chat?

00:16:17.159 --> 00:16:18.419
Listening to both sides brings clarity.

00:16:19.039 --> 00:16:19.820
Let me introduce you.

00:16:20.000 --> 00:16:20.980
This is Mr. Liang.

00:16:22.019 --> 00:16:23.480
Get to know each other.

00:16:23.860 --> 00:16:24.559
Mr. Liang.

00:16:24.620 --> 00:16:26.840
Is he that big star's dad?

00:16:26.840 --> 00:16:27.320
Yes.

00:16:27.700 --> 00:16:28.840
That's right.

00:16:28.919 --> 00:16:30.259
You know this too?

00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:31.940
How could I not know?

00:16:32.799 --> 00:16:34.659
Everyone's talking about it.

00:16:36.360 --> 00:16:37.220
Uncle Liang,

00:16:37.559 --> 00:16:39.240
I wanted to ask you,

00:16:39.519 --> 00:16:40.799
is it possible for me

00:16:40.860 --> 00:16:42.019
to invest in Miss Bai's

00:16:42.080 --> 00:16:43.519
movie production?

00:16:43.700 --> 00:16:45.100
Absolutely!

00:16:45.460 --> 00:16:46.019
Brother,

00:16:46.059 --> 00:16:46.980
let's add each other on WeChat.

00:16:47.399 --> 00:16:48.820
I'll scan you.

00:16:50.399 --> 00:16:51.379
What are you doing?

00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:52.620
I say,

00:16:52.759 --> 00:16:53.500
you two...

00:16:53.620 --> 00:16:54.620
I'm telling you two, this is called

00:16:54.700 --> 00:16:55.720
dereliction of duty.

00:16:56.100 --> 00:16:56.879
That seems inaccurate.

00:16:57.419 --> 00:16:58.559
Inviting a wolf into the house.

00:16:59.799 --> 00:17:00.340
Not that bad.

00:17:00.980 --> 00:17:02.039
Treason and defecting.

00:17:02.919 --> 00:17:03.679
Too serious, that's a huge crime.

00:17:04.900 --> 00:17:06.180
Colluding.

00:17:06.599 --> 00:17:07.299
That's the one.

00:17:09.140 --> 00:17:11.079
This must be that

00:17:11.099 --> 00:17:13.079
famous matchmaker,

00:17:14.259 --> 00:17:16.180
Auntie Cai, right?

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:17.619
He knows that too.

00:17:19.400 --> 00:17:20.519
Auntie Cai,

00:17:21.019 --> 00:17:22.680
I'm actually single.

00:17:23.279 --> 00:17:25.839
Could you introduce me

00:17:25.900 --> 00:17:27.859
to a suitable girl?

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:29.460
You want a partner?

00:17:29.460 --> 00:17:30.359
Yes.

00:17:30.779 --> 00:17:32.220
Absolutely!

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:34.640
I'll go get the photos for you right now.

00:17:35.220 --> 00:17:36.480
Pick whoever you like. Just wait.

00:17:36.480 --> 00:17:36.900
Just a moment.

00:17:36.900 --> 00:17:37.799
Hold on.

00:17:40.660 --> 00:17:42.359
You two uncles,

00:17:42.579 --> 00:17:43.660
do you think

00:17:43.880 --> 00:17:44.900
my teacher

00:17:45.259 --> 00:17:45.940
will

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:47.339
see me today?

00:17:47.559 --> 00:17:48.579
No problem.

00:17:49.740 --> 00:17:50.220
Let's go.

00:17:55.119 --> 00:17:55.619
Professor Fan

00:17:55.680 --> 00:17:56.480
What are you all

00:17:56.920 --> 00:17:57.799
trying to do?

00:17:59.180 --> 00:18:00.920
Professor Fan, what are you doing?

00:18:01.400 --> 00:18:02.500
The poor kid is sincere

00:18:02.500 --> 00:18:03.599
and came all this way.

00:18:04.259 --> 00:18:06.220
What's wrong with letting the kid speak?

00:18:06.619 --> 00:18:07.559
Exactly.

00:18:07.700 --> 00:18:08.700
As far as I know,

00:18:08.759 --> 00:18:10.460
this is all just a misunderstanding.

00:18:10.460 --> 00:18:11.740
It'll be fine once we talk it out.

00:18:11.740 --> 00:18:12.339
That's right.

00:18:12.500 --> 00:18:13.839
There is no misunderstanding!

00:18:14.559 --> 00:18:15.460
Cheating on an exam.

00:18:16.000 --> 00:18:17.279
If I caught it today,

00:18:17.380 --> 00:18:18.619
I'd still confiscate the paper.

00:18:19.519 --> 00:18:20.319
Professor...

00:18:20.359 --> 00:18:21.000
I actually...

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:21.619
Please.

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:22.619
Get out.

00:18:22.819 --> 00:18:23.460
I won't listen.

00:18:24.640 --> 00:18:26.019
You all saw it.

00:18:26.099 --> 00:18:28.019
My professor's state today...

00:18:28.299 --> 00:18:29.680
he won't let me speak.

00:18:29.960 --> 00:18:30.819
Come on, Professor Fan.

00:18:33.299 --> 00:18:34.019
Professor.

00:18:34.460 --> 00:18:35.700
Please don't be angry.

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:36.940
I'll go.

00:18:37.440 --> 00:18:38.680
I'll go, okay?

00:18:39.099 --> 00:18:40.039
I'm leaving.

00:18:41.660 --> 00:18:42.119
Kid,

00:18:42.180 --> 00:18:42.779
where are you going?

00:18:43.019 --> 00:18:44.079
We haven't had a proper chat yet.

00:18:44.140 --> 00:18:45.180
Look at this girl.

00:18:46.420 --> 00:18:47.900
I'll come back tomorrow.

00:18:47.960 --> 00:18:48.559
Go!

00:18:48.839 --> 00:18:49.960
Don't ever come back!

00:18:51.259 --> 00:18:52.400
Professor Fan, what are you doing?

00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:53.000
Go!

00:18:53.740 --> 00:18:54.400
No one's listening to you.

00:18:54.700 --> 00:18:55.220
Kid,

00:18:55.400 --> 00:18:56.740
come to Auntie's room to see photos.

00:18:56.900 --> 00:18:57.559
Come, follow me.

00:18:57.559 --> 00:18:58.000
Then I...

00:18:58.039 --> 00:18:59.079
I'll go too.

00:18:59.180 --> 00:18:59.960
Wait a minute.

00:18:59.960 --> 00:19:01.500
You haven't accepted my WeChat request yet.

00:19:05.039 --> 00:19:05.819
Why aren't you leaving?

00:19:06.319 --> 00:19:07.519
Where am I supposed to go?

00:19:08.059 --> 00:19:09.220
This is my room too.

00:19:25.160 --> 00:19:25.900
Grandpa Fan

00:19:26.200 --> 00:19:27.859
Can you get full eating so little?

00:19:27.940 --> 00:19:28.640
I can't eat.

00:19:28.740 --> 00:19:29.720
I'm full from anger.

00:19:30.599 --> 00:19:32.220
Please don't be angry.

00:19:32.619 --> 00:19:33.460
If you get angry,

00:19:33.660 --> 00:19:35.119
you'll fall for He Ziqiang's trap.

00:19:35.339 --> 00:19:36.539
When I was in high school,

00:19:36.819 --> 00:19:38.039
I also made a mistake once.

00:19:38.160 --> 00:19:39.519
The teacher criticized me by name.

00:19:39.839 --> 00:19:41.319
I held a grudge for a long time.

00:19:41.480 --> 00:19:42.339
All I wanted was

00:19:42.400 --> 00:19:43.500
to get into a good university,

00:19:43.720 --> 00:19:44.680
just to spite him later.

00:19:44.980 --> 00:19:46.119
So, I think

00:19:46.359 --> 00:19:48.059
He Ziqiang is here to upset you.

00:19:50.220 --> 00:19:50.799
Child,

00:19:50.960 --> 00:19:52.420
your analysis makes sense.

00:19:52.980 --> 00:19:54.839
I've never looked at this issue

00:19:54.839 --> 00:19:55.859
from a student's perspective.

00:19:56.299 --> 00:19:57.400
Later on,

00:19:57.819 --> 00:19:59.000
when I saw that teacher,

00:19:59.420 --> 00:20:00.700
not only did I not spite him,

00:20:01.059 --> 00:20:02.500
but I actually felt quite regretful.

00:20:03.779 --> 00:20:04.559
Why is that?

00:20:05.440 --> 00:20:06.339
Originally, I

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:07.900
wanted to make some snide remarks.

00:20:08.059 --> 00:20:09.119
But unexpectedly, the teacher

00:20:09.119 --> 00:20:09.960
beat me to it.

00:20:10.720 --> 00:20:11.859
He made snide remarks first.

00:20:12.319 --> 00:20:12.720
No,

00:20:12.720 --> 00:20:13.160
that's not it.

00:20:14.099 --> 00:20:15.099
He asked me

00:20:15.359 --> 00:20:16.619
how I was doing,

00:20:16.819 --> 00:20:18.460
if I was used to living away from home,

00:20:18.660 --> 00:20:20.220
and if I was getting along with people.

00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:22.519
It made me feel quite ashamed.

00:20:22.700 --> 00:20:24.119
I realized I was in the wrong.

00:20:24.119 --> 00:20:25.339
The teacher meant well for me,

00:20:25.859 --> 00:20:26.900
but I was being petty,

00:20:27.160 --> 00:20:28.539
holding a grudge against him for years.

00:20:28.740 --> 00:20:29.859
Even now,

00:20:29.859 --> 00:20:31.539
I visit that teacher every year I go home.

00:20:34.619 --> 00:20:35.180
Grandpa Fan.

00:20:36.420 --> 00:20:36.980
Grandpa Fan?

00:20:38.119 --> 00:20:38.779
How about

00:20:38.859 --> 00:20:39.960
I walk you back?

00:20:40.099 --> 00:20:40.880
No need.

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:42.640
I want to sit by myself for a while.

00:20:42.759 --> 00:20:43.559
Alright, you sit.

00:20:43.720 --> 00:20:44.619
I'll go eat over there.

00:21:02.519 --> 00:21:03.940
I didn't expect,

00:21:04.279 --> 00:21:04.960
Teacher,

00:21:05.079 --> 00:21:06.940
that you would reach out to me first.

00:21:07.759 --> 00:21:09.220
I didn't expect it myself either.

00:21:09.759 --> 00:21:10.480
Teacher,

00:21:10.940 --> 00:21:12.640
when I was expelled back then,

00:21:12.980 --> 00:21:14.720
it was my own doing.

00:21:15.000 --> 00:21:16.519
It had nothing to do with you.

00:21:17.559 --> 00:21:18.720
Since that's the case,

00:21:19.319 --> 00:21:20.859
why did you come all the way here

00:21:20.859 --> 00:21:22.299
just to annoy me endlessly?

00:21:23.200 --> 00:21:25.240
It was because of what you said.

00:21:25.519 --> 00:21:25.980
Me?

00:21:26.039 --> 00:21:27.579
What did I say?

00:21:28.599 --> 00:21:30.720
When I was being expelled,

00:21:31.059 --> 00:21:31.700
you said,

00:21:32.200 --> 00:21:34.240
"This child is a lost cause."

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:36.900
"No morals, no bottom line."

00:21:36.960 --> 00:21:38.019
"For his whole life,"

00:21:38.220 --> 00:21:40.259
"he won't amount to anything."

00:21:41.299 --> 00:21:42.099
These words,

00:21:42.460 --> 00:21:43.640
I heard them all.

00:21:44.259 --> 00:21:44.619
No,

00:21:44.660 --> 00:21:45.200
I...

00:21:45.240 --> 00:21:47.039
did I say such things?

00:21:48.180 --> 00:21:49.799
Why don't I remember that?

00:21:50.660 --> 00:21:52.319
You may not remember,

00:21:52.819 --> 00:21:54.220
but do you know

00:21:54.359 --> 00:21:56.299
how much those words provoked me,

00:21:56.559 --> 00:21:57.700
do you have any idea?

00:22:03.420 --> 00:22:04.079
Child,

00:22:05.420 --> 00:22:06.420
Back then, I

00:22:06.819 --> 00:22:07.619
was wrong.

00:22:08.240 --> 00:22:09.960
Is it because you saw

00:22:10.319 --> 00:22:11.299
me now,

00:22:11.420 --> 00:22:12.700
and all this,

00:22:13.099 --> 00:22:14.920
that you think you were wrong?

00:22:15.160 --> 00:22:16.059
No.

00:22:16.400 --> 00:22:17.740
It's not because

00:22:17.779 --> 00:22:18.799
I see you now

00:22:18.799 --> 00:22:19.680
that I say this.

00:22:19.980 --> 00:22:21.099
But because I realized

00:22:21.319 --> 00:22:22.440
that as a teacher,

00:22:22.980 --> 00:22:24.579
I shouldn't make

00:22:24.859 --> 00:22:26.079
such a conclusion about a student.

00:22:28.460 --> 00:22:29.200
Your teacher

00:22:29.640 --> 00:22:30.880
sincerely apologizes to you.

00:22:31.700 --> 00:22:32.680
Teacher,

00:22:32.799 --> 00:22:34.519
Please don't be like this.

00:22:34.559 --> 00:22:35.339
If you apologize,

00:22:35.339 --> 00:22:37.359
I can't say the rest.

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:39.519
Say whatever you have to say.

00:22:40.059 --> 00:22:41.319
I am ready

00:22:41.500 --> 00:22:42.859
to accept all your criticism.

00:22:43.619 --> 00:22:45.279
It's not criticism.

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:48.000
I need to apologize.

00:22:48.720 --> 00:22:49.339
Teacher,

00:22:50.000 --> 00:22:51.460
I apologize to you.

00:22:52.039 --> 00:22:52.920
I'm sorry.

00:22:52.920 --> 00:22:54.660
I should be the one apologizing.

00:22:54.799 --> 00:22:55.799
It's me.

00:22:56.779 --> 00:22:57.680
Listen to me, child.

00:22:57.680 --> 00:22:58.400
Listen to me.

00:22:59.119 --> 00:23:00.160
Back then, I

00:23:00.440 --> 00:23:01.440
really shouldn't have

00:23:01.440 --> 00:23:02.759
made that conclusion about you.

00:23:03.220 --> 00:23:04.039
Teacher,

00:23:04.440 --> 00:23:07.000
Your conclusion wasn't wrong.

00:23:07.960 --> 00:23:08.440
I...

00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:09.440
I shouldn't have

00:23:09.519 --> 00:23:11.380
borrowed a luxury car to trick you.

00:23:12.440 --> 00:23:13.119
What?

00:23:13.559 --> 00:23:14.140
You...

00:23:14.599 --> 00:23:16.119
Your luxury car is borrowed?

00:23:16.960 --> 00:23:17.759
Yes.

00:23:18.559 --> 00:23:20.180
And this suit,

00:23:21.420 --> 00:23:22.099
belt,

00:23:23.079 --> 00:23:23.880
watch,

00:23:24.420 --> 00:23:25.579
and gold chain.

00:23:25.880 --> 00:23:28.579
I borrowed them all from friends and relatives.

00:23:30.720 --> 00:23:32.599
Just to prove myself

00:23:32.819 --> 00:23:34.140
in front of you.

00:23:38.059 --> 00:23:39.460
So now you...

00:23:40.099 --> 00:23:40.759
Teacher,

00:23:41.859 --> 00:23:43.319
You have a poisonous tongue.

00:23:44.559 --> 00:23:45.940
I've achieved nothing.

00:23:46.059 --> 00:23:47.940
I failed your mentorship.

00:23:52.119 --> 00:23:52.799
Child,

00:23:53.319 --> 00:23:54.099
Don't be like that.

00:23:54.980 --> 00:23:56.299
I'll make another prediction.

00:23:56.839 --> 00:23:57.619
In the future,

00:23:58.039 --> 00:23:59.359
you will definitely succeed.

00:24:02.700 --> 00:24:03.500
Great.

00:24:05.160 --> 00:24:06.559
So it was all fake.

00:24:06.839 --> 00:24:07.319
Then...

00:24:07.380 --> 00:24:08.400
all those photos of girls

00:24:08.480 --> 00:24:09.400
I showed you for nothing.

00:24:09.900 --> 00:24:10.180
Wait,

00:24:10.180 --> 00:24:12.380
What about investing in my daughter's movie?

00:24:12.380 --> 00:24:13.160
Is there still a chance?

00:24:13.599 --> 00:24:14.700
There's a chance.

00:24:14.759 --> 00:24:15.900
Wait ten years.

00:24:16.059 --> 00:24:17.799
After I've made my mark,

00:24:17.880 --> 00:24:18.799
I'll come back.

00:24:18.900 --> 00:24:19.480
I'll just

00:24:19.480 --> 00:24:20.420
block him.

00:24:20.420 --> 00:24:20.799
Right.

00:24:20.859 --> 00:24:22.099
The teacher's conclusion

00:24:22.160 --> 00:24:23.099
is never wrong.

00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:27.059
Where is Ms. Liu?

00:24:27.359 --> 00:24:28.579
Isn't she with you?

00:24:28.740 --> 00:24:29.440
No.

00:24:29.519 --> 00:24:30.200
What's up?

00:24:30.220 --> 00:24:31.799
Something happened! Something big!

00:24:31.799 --> 00:24:33.319
What happened?

00:24:33.359 --> 00:24:35.759
Ms. Liu's celebrity student Zhang Tianyu

00:24:36.460 --> 00:24:37.640
his reputation is in ruins.

00:24:38.299 --> 00:24:39.759
Reported by Chaoyang Residents.

00:24:39.839 --> 00:24:41.140
Let's go tell Grandma Liu.

00:24:41.140 --> 00:24:41.799
Quick, yes.

00:24:41.839 --> 00:24:42.240
Right.

00:24:42.859 --> 00:24:43.819
What do you mean "in ruins"?

00:24:44.839 --> 00:24:45.859
How did the house collapse?

00:24:46.119 --> 00:24:47.079
Did it hit anyone?

00:24:47.079 --> 00:24:48.019
I don't know.